<HEADLINE>
FT  02 OCT 93 / International Company News: Murdoch completes NY Post
acquisition
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By AP-DJ
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   NEW YORK
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
MR RUPERT Murdoch has completed his purchase of the New York Post newspaper,
AP-DJ reports from New York. The purchase, by News Corp subsidiary New
America Publishing, follows ratification of new agreements by production
workers. News Corp bought the Post from the estate of Mr Peter Kalikow, the
paper's former owner, for around Dollars 25m.
