                         10 years                              25 years
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Abbey Life                 36,700   Equitable Life              208,020
Equitable Life             36,649   Cornhill Assurance          206,241
Rothschild Asset Mgmt      36,306   Albany Life                 205,937
Scottish Mutual            36,113   Prosperity Life*            205,286
Family Assurance           35,878   Wesleyan &amp; General          204,937
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
