                         10 years                              25 years
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Combined Insurance         32,463   Royal London                175,718
Providence Capitol         32,277   Combined Insurance          175,387
Royal London               31,294   Gartmore                    175,072
Refuge Assurance*          31,222   Acuma Life                  174,365
