Metallgesellschaft, and has international mining interests.
Instead of the public offer, Metall has issued 15.9m shares at CDollars
10.75 each to the parent in exchange for the smelting interests. This raises
Metallgesellschaft's interest in Metall to 68 per cent from 60.5 per cent.
