for the April year-end, which were down at Pounds 2.21m (Pounds 3.93m).
It said yesterday that sales volumes and margins had fallen further since
then. In an attempt to counter that it was pushing up prices and cutting
costs. It said its new freezing plant, which had suffered commissioning
problems, was now working satisfactorily.
